Running the pipeline
Open your terminal, navigate to the folder, and run:
cd path/to/run\ project
python3 runner_pipeline.py
Or just press the Run button in VS Code with runner_pipeline.py open.

Expected output
When it completes successfully you should see all 6 steps with ✔ checkmarks and a 5-row preview table. Two files will be created inside a running_output/ folder that the script generates automatically:
